CREATE TABLE grades (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    assignment_id INT,

CREATE TABLE assessments (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    assessment_type VARCHAR(50),
    assessment_date DATE,
    assessment_result INT
);
